  "title": "Jason Wei：AI 的三大趋势——智能商品化、验证者定律与智能的锯齿状边缘",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNjkzNDMzMA==&mid=2247484351&idx=1&sn=ff576657b7e1b6b3e511f4e51631176b",
  "date": "2025-11-03 06:16:00",
